    "The 3rd year classes consisted of a total of 39 students, of which 20 (18F and 2M) were assigned to the control group while 19 (17F and 2M) were assigned to the treatment group.",
    "The 5th year consisted of 37 students, of whom 19 (17F and 2M) were assigned to the control group and 18 (13F and 5M) were assigned to the treatment group.",
    "All the students had access to the internet either through a smartphone or through a computer.",
    "In every class, the English curriculum was composed of two main parts: 3 hours of weekly lectures and 1-2 hours of weekly homework and selfstudy.",
    "We intervened on homework and self-study."
